Subject: [depends] Fix missing VERSION macro in qrencode 4.1.1

qrencode 4.1.1's autotools config does not expose VERSION in config.h, but
qrencode.c references it in QRcode_APIVersionString().

Use PACKAGE_VERSION as a fallback so the library builds cleanly.

diff --git a/qrencode.c b/qrencode.c
--- a/qrencode.c
+++ b/qrencode.c
@@ -929,7 +929,11 @@ void QRcode_APIVersion(int *major_version, int *minor_version, int *micro_version
 
 char *QRcode_APIVersionString(void)
 {
+#ifdef VERSION
 	return VERSION;
+#else
+	return PACKAGE_VERSION;
+#endif
 }
 
 void QRcode_clearCache(void)
 {
